# Middleware - function that fires on the in-between before the response goes out.
    express.json(): looks for a request body and turns it into a "req.body"
    app.use("/", express.json()) (first argument is optional, so it can look like: app.use(express.json()))

# Request Body - (req body): app.use

# Express Router - Enables us to modularize our routes in express

